text: Chaudhary Sunder Singh is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Lok Sabha, the lower house of the Parliament of India from the Phillaur constituency of Punjab as a member of the Indian National Congress. ==References== Category:Indian National Congress politicians Category:Lok Sabha members from Punjab, India Category:7th Lok Sabha members Category:Possibly living people Category:Year of birth missing
